      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car. It\u2019s been a fantastic daily driver and is still in really solid, reliable shape! I\u2019ve truly loved driving this beauty, and I think you will too. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next big adventure. I'm more than happy to chat, answer any questions, or have you over for a test drive. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
