    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera remains a purist\u2019s benchmark, featuring the 3.6L flat-six mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. Mechanically robust, the M96 powerplant has been proactively serviced with an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a high-flow water pump to ensure thermal efficiency. The chassis retains its composure via Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing variable damping rates that remain sharp under lateral load. The naturally aspirated induction note is unfiltered, and the limited-slip differential provides excellent exit traction. Recent service includes a full fluid flush with Motul 8100 X-cess and a borescope inspection showing clean cylinder walls. Minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited road use, but the drivetrain is dialed in for the next apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
