      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained example that strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior presents beautifully in its original paint, showing only minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the passenger-side mirror housing, consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the upholstery is free of rips or stains, though there is light softening on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All power features, including the sunroof, heated seats, and infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is ready for the road. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent invoice showing a fresh oil service, new engine air filters, and a brake fluid flush. The transmission shifts crisp and the engine pulls strongly without any hesitation or warning lights. The tires are matching set with plenty of tread depth remaining. This is a dependable, honest vehicle that requires nothing but a new owner. Includes two keys and a folder of service receipts.",
